 &lt;BR&gt; 
3) Profit / (Loss) before tax from continuing operations for the quarter ended 31.03.2026 is Rs. 28.23 crore &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
4) Profit / (Loss) before tax from discontinued operations for the quarter ended 31.03.2026 is Rs. 0.01 crore &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
5) Total Profit / (Loss) before Tax for the quarter ended 31.03.2026 is Rs. 28.24 crore &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
6) Profit / (Loss) before tax from continuing operations for the year ended 31.03.2026 is Rs. 31.45 crore &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
7) Profit / (Loss) before tax from discontinued operations for the year ended 31.03.2026 is Rs. 0.02 crore &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
8) Total Profit / (Loss) before for the year ended 31.03.2026 is Rs. 31.47 crore &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
9) Unallocated Assets for the year ended 31.03.2026 includes Textile Discontinued Operations (Foreign Subsidiary) : Rs. 1704.44 crore = Rs. 1703.40 crore + Rs. 1.04 crore &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
10) Unallocated Liabilities for the year ended 31.03.2026 includes Textile Discontinued Operations (Foreign Subsidiary) : Rs. 22.46 crore = Rs. 21.52 crore + Rs. 0.94 crore &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
11) Segment Revenue excludes unallocated revenue of Rs. 3.25 crores and Rs. 12.99 crores for the quarter and year ended March 31, 2026, respectively. &lt;BR&gt; 
